patthana14.36:4.1: Sauttaraṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca naanuttaro dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. #1
patthana14.36:5.1: Anuttaraṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca naanuttaro dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana14.36:5.2: Anuttaraṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nasauttaro dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana14.36:5.3: Anuttaraṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nasauttaro ca naanuttaro ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā. #3
patthana14.36:6.1: Sauttarañca anuttarañca dhammaṃ paṭicca naanuttaro dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. #1
patthana14.36:7.1: Hetuyā pañca, ārammaṇe dve … pe … avigate pañca.
